106
00:08:19,950 --> 00:08:21,390
Lord Yang

107
00:08:21,790 --> 00:08:23,910
handled similar cases before.

108
00:08:24,470 --> 00:08:26,030
He arranged refugees in provinces

109
00:08:26,030 --> 00:08:27,760
near the Imperial Capital.

110
00:08:28,910 --> 00:08:30,310
The young and strong

111
00:08:30,430 --> 00:08:32,600
participated in the local construction.

112
00:08:32,600 --> 00:08:34,659
Each province received cheap labor.

113
00:08:34,710 --> 00:08:37,710
It's natural for them to take care of the old, the weak,

114
00:08:37,830 --> 00:08:39,320
the women, and children.

115
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:45,670
That's a good idea.

116
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:48,610
Let's do it then.

117
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:53,590
Anything else?

118
00:08:54,750 --> 00:08:56,190
The locusts have been spreading lately.

119
00:08:56,190 --> 00:08:59,450
We haven't sprayed medicine to prevent those insects yet.

120
00:08:59,510 --> 00:09:01,910
This medicine has a small amount of poison.

121
00:09:02,310 --> 00:09:04,410
Lord Canxing. Please make a decision.

122
00:09:04,410 --> 00:09:06,360
The new bandits are rampant in Xinji Province.

123
00:09:06,360 --> 00:09:07,830
The Governor asked for a loan to manage it.

124
00:09:07,830 --> 00:09:10,980
But the war in Yuanzhou is around the corner. The treasury is tight.

125
00:09:10,980 --> 00:09:13,090
Please make a decision.

126
00:09:13,710 --> 00:09:15,020
Okay.

127
00:09:20,390 --> 00:09:22,550
My head is numb.

128
00:09:23,630 --> 00:09:25,190
Lord Yang Minghua

129
