130
00:09:28,350 --> 00:09:31,510
There are many government affairs now.

131
00:09:32,110 --> 00:09:34,320
I can't figure out

132
00:09:34,390 --> 00:09:37,990
all of them for now.

133
00:09:38,590 --> 00:09:40,110
Go get me the documents of Lord Yang Minghua's

134
00:09:40,110 --> 00:09:43,040
handling of government affairs in the past few years

135
00:09:44,790 --> 00:09:46,110
for me to refer to.

136
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:47,750
Yes.

137
00:09:52,270 --> 00:09:55,200
Princess Ka Dan has moved to Zichuan Ning's Mansion.

138
00:09:57,590 --> 00:09:59,830
Lord Ge Yingxing led his army

139
00:09:59,950 --> 00:10:01,670
to go to Yuanzhou last night.

140
00:10:02,040 --> 00:10:03,170
Di Lin followed him.

141
00:10:03,510 --> 00:10:06,310
They should have left the Imperial Capital by now.

142
00:10:06,470 --> 00:10:10,030
Lord Chieftain is busy with government affairs.

143
00:10:10,390 --> 00:10:11,660
He even called out the documents

144
00:10:11,660 --> 00:10:13,990
you handled a few years ago for reference.

145
00:10:14,590 --> 00:10:16,580
But it didn't help much.

146
00:10:16,870 --> 00:10:19,230
It seems that Lord Chieftain

147
00:10:20,080 --> 00:10:24,000
wants you to leave seclusion early to deal with government affairs.

148
00:10:24,630 --> 00:10:26,410
I should have taken my collections

149
00:10:26,410 --> 00:10:29,060
out and sorted them out long ago.

150
00:10:29,350 --> 00:10:30,910
But I didn't have time.

151
00:10:31,920 --> 00:10:32,930
To be honest,

152
00:10:33,560 --> 00:10:35,600
I have to thank Lord Chieftain

153
00:10:35,630 --> 00:10:37,690
for making me reflect on my mistakes.

154
00:10:40,920 --> 00:10:43,320
By the way, My Lord, there is one more thing.

155
00:10:50,130 --> 00:10:53,580
