156
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:56,260
They wanted to send it to Ge Yingxing.

157
00:11:05,950 --> 00:11:07,060
This is the safety information

158
00:11:07,060 --> 00:11:09,260
sent by Princess Ka Dan to the North Clan

159
00:11:09,660 --> 00:11:12,530
