160
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:19,140
Everyone has been in our mansion for days.

161
00:11:19,140 --> 00:11:21,060
Lady Ning is in a good mood today.

162
00:11:21,230 --> 00:11:23,830
So she specially prepared gifts for you.

163
00:11:24,390 --> 00:11:25,190
Lord Luo Jie.

164
00:11:26,950 --> 00:11:27,680
Lord Ming Yu.

165
00:11:28,670 --> 00:11:29,870
These are for you.

166
00:11:30,030 --> 00:11:33,130
They are said to be the best military books in the world.

167
00:11:33,160 --> 00:11:34,820
Isn't this Lord Xiu's porn...

168
00:11:37,100 --> 00:11:39,020
Anything good happened? Why...

169
00:11:41,150 --> 00:11:42,230
Isn't this mine?

170
00:11:42,660 --> 00:11:43,410
Mei, go on.

171
00:11:43,840 --> 00:11:44,640
It's mine now.

172
00:11:45,430 --> 00:11:46,160
Give it to me.

173
00:11:46,700 --> 00:11:48,660
Princess Ka Dan, you just came to the Imperial Capital.

174
00:11:48,660 --> 00:11:50,380
