175
00:11:50,760 --> 00:11:51,660
This is for you.

176
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,350
I don't think it's appropriate.

177
00:11:53,350 --> 00:11:53,950
It's fine.

178
00:11:55,670 --> 00:11:57,590
Even if it's to make Lady Ning happy,

179
00:11:57,590 --> 00:11:58,650
