180
00:11:59,750 --> 00:12:00,350
It's fine.

181
00:12:00,620 --> 00:12:02,830
Lord Baichuan, you just recovered.

182
00:12:03,010 --> 00:12:04,820
You should buy something to nourish yourself.

183
00:12:04,820 --> 00:12:05,680
This is for you.

184
00:12:07,950 --> 00:12:10,500
Why does the money smell weird?

185
00:12:11,150 --> 00:12:12,150
It smells like...

186
00:12:16,230 --> 00:12:17,990
Mei, this is for you.

187
00:12:18,010 --> 00:12:19,210
This is my money.

188
00:12:19,900 --> 00:12:22,630
The private money that I've kept for seven years.

189
00:12:26,590 --> 00:12:28,800
Zichuan Ning, wait and see.

190
00:12:29,770 --> 00:12:32,210
I don't want the money back.

191
00:12:38,990 --> 00:12:41,470
Did Lord Xiu offend Lady Ning?

192
00:12:47,780 --> 00:12:48,580
Zichuan Ning.

193
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:51,440
You pretend you can't see me?

194
00:12:52,150 --> 00:12:52,630
Okay.

195
00:12:55,210 --> 00:12:56,800
This rouge...

196
00:13:00,710 --> 00:13:04,030
Ka Dan, the Imperial Capital has a lot of delicious food.

197
00:13:04,250 --> 00:13:06,250
I'll bring them all to you next time.

198
00:13:06,400 --> 00:13:07,420
What is this?

199
00:13:08,040 --> 00:13:09,550
This seems to be the most expensive

200
00:13:09,550 --> 00:13:11,810
rose serum in the Imperial Capital.

201
00:13:13,370 --> 00:13:14,670
It smells so good.

202
00:13:17,670 --> 00:13:19,190
I should have

203
00:13:19,190 --> 00:13:20,990
changed the cosmetics long ago.

204
00:13:21,190 --> 00:13:22,480
I don't like them anymore.

205
00:13:22,480 --> 00:13:24,000
All of them should be replaced with new ones.

206
00:13:24,000 --> 00:13:25,330
Miss Baichuan, join me.

207
00:13:25,460 --> 00:13:26,100
Sure.

208
00:13:27,500 --> 00:13:28,780
What is this?

209
00:13:29,160 --> 00:13:30,720
Pearl handbag.

210
00:13:31,990 --> 00:13:33,670
It's made of the craftsmanship of the Lin family.

211
00:13:33,670 --> 00:13:36,470
I think there are only two in the Imperial Capital.

212
00:13:36,640 --> 00:13:38,690
I'll tear it now.

213
00:13:40,990 --> 00:13:43,310
We can buy some handbags.

214
00:13:46,110 --> 00:13:46,870
Yes.

215
00:13:48,130 --> 00:13:50,410
The most important thing for Ning

216
00:13:51,030 --> 00:13:52,710
is me, Brother Xiu.

217
00:13:52,800 --> 00:13:56,020
Lord Xiu, aren't you too confident?

218
00:13:56,470 --> 00:13:57,750
Who's Lord Xiu?

219
00:14:03,500 --> 00:14:04,420
Zichuan Ning.

220
00:14:04,670 --> 00:14:06,930
If you continue to pretend not to hear me,

221
00:14:07,150 --> 00:14:09,860
I'll jump from here.

222
00:14:10,100 --> 00:14:11,530
I'll count to three.

223
00:14:13,990 --> 00:14:14,390
Three.

224
00:14:14,970 --> 00:14:16,280
Let's pack up and go.

225
00:14:16,880 --> 00:14:17,550
Two.

226
00:14:18,150 --> 00:14:20,750
If we're late, we won't be able to buy good ones.

227
00:14:20,920 --> 00:14:21,560
One.

228
00:14:24,910 --> 00:14:25,990
One.

229
00:14:26,790 --> 00:14:27,960
Come on.

230
00:14:28,590 --> 00:14:29,840
Wait and see.

231
00:14:37,880 --> 00:14:40,280
Why do you look worse than me?

232
00:14:40,850 --> 00:14:43,680
Yes, I'm badly hurt.

233
00:14:44,270 --> 00:14:45,750
I have nothing now.

234
00:14:46,980 --> 00:14:48,980
If I don't want to live on the street,

235
00:14:49,970 --> 00:14:52,370
I can only live in the Chieftain's Mansion.

236
00:14:52,790 --> 00:14:54,320
I don't care where you live.

237
00:14:54,340 --> 00:14:55,940
Let's get down to business.

238
00:14:56,350 --> 00:14:58,070
I'm going to live in the Chieftain's Mansion.

239
00:14:58,070 --> 00:14:59,550
Let's get down to business.

240
00:14:59,550 --> 00:15:00,500
I'm talking business.

241
00:15:00,500 --> 00:15:01,230
How?

242
00:15:05,280 --> 00:15:06,920
This is the task given to me by Lord Ge.

243
00:15:06,920 --> 00:15:08,450
I can only see the documents

244
00:15:08,490 --> 00:15:09,690
handled by Yang Minghua over the past few years

245
00:15:09,690 --> 00:15:11,820
by living in the Chieftain's Mansion.

246
00:15:11,830 --> 00:15:14,450
Then I can check what cards he has.

247
00:15:14,670 --> 00:15:16,950
I am the Deputy Commander of the Royal Escorts.

248
00:15:16,950 --> 00:15:19,610
It's reasonable for me to live there, but you...

249
00:15:22,670 --> 00:15:24,430
Didn't I quarrel with Ning?

250
00:15:24,430 --> 00:15:26,460
I'm kicked out and homeless.

251
00:15:27,070 --> 00:15:28,910
Isn't it reasonable

252
00:15:29,670 --> 00:15:31,200
to ask my uncle to take me in?

253
00:15:31,630 --> 00:15:32,310
Good.

254
00:15:32,750 --> 00:15:34,950
Tell him at the family banquet tonight.

255
00:15:35,210 --> 00:15:36,340
The family banquet?

256
00:15:37,460 --> 00:15:38,660
What family banquet?

257
00:15:38,950 --> 00:15:43,190
Here's the thing. Mei told Baichuan.

258
00:15:43,640 --> 00:15:45,760
Baichuan told Luo Jie.

259
00:15:46,030 --> 00:15:47,880
Luo Jie told Ming Yu.

260
00:15:47,910 --> 00:15:49,590
Ming Yu told me.

261
00:15:49,590 --> 00:15:52,150
Then he asked me to tell you

262
00:15:52,190 --> 00:15:55,720
that you're attending Lord Canxing's family banquet tonight.

263
00:15:57,270 --> 00:15:58,030
I see.

264
00:15:58,350 --> 00:16:01,140
Zichuan Ning told me to attend the family banquet.

265
00:16:01,140 --> 00:16:01,940
That's right.

266
00:16:07,200 --> 00:16:08,750
Uncle, the meat is delicious.

267
00:16:08,750 --> 00:16:09,590
Eat more.

268
00:16:13,830 --> 00:16:15,560
I think this is also delicious.

269
00:16:15,990 --> 00:16:16,550
Delicious.

270
00:16:16,550 --> 00:16:17,350
Ning.

271
00:16:18,890 --> 00:16:20,740
You have to make Xiu full, okay?

272
00:16:21,670 --> 00:16:23,120
Let him eat more.

273
00:16:23,440 --> 00:16:24,830
This is a family banquet after all.

274
00:16:24,830 --> 00:16:26,240
You can't let him starve.

275
00:16:26,550 --> 00:16:27,550
Uncle, who is Xiu?

276
00:16:28,310 --> 00:16:30,110
There are only the two of us here.

277
00:16:30,910 --> 00:16:32,970
My Lord, this is not a family banquet.

278
00:16:33,240 --> 00:16:35,640
If Ning doesn't consider me as her brother,

