Zichuan Xiu.

557
00:33:06,150 --> 00:33:08,950
My Lord, I've verified it. It's indeed a private mine.

558
00:33:08,950 --> 00:33:11,680
And all the income flows to the Imperial Capital.

559
00:33:13,390 --> 00:33:14,910
Have the explosion points been set up?

560
00:33:14,910 --> 00:33:16,110
Everything is ready.

561
00:33:16,350 --> 00:33:16,980
Blow it up.

562
00:33:26,590 --> 00:33:27,580
So troublesome.

563
00:33:29,830 --> 00:33:31,500
You want me to fake Lord Yang's order?

564
00:33:31,500 --> 00:33:34,030
This is Yang Minghua's private food storage.

565
00:33:34,040 --> 00:33:35,500
What do you think he wants?

566
00:33:36,390 --> 00:33:39,020
There are 200,000 refugees outside the Imperial Capital.

567
00:33:39,020 --> 00:33:40,480
They won't starve to death

568
00:33:40,850 --> 00:33:42,400
if we distribute grains.

569
00:33:42,880 --> 00:33:43,610
Understand?

570
00:33:45,500 --> 00:33:46,430
You want me to go?

571
00:33:46,940 --> 00:33:48,340
Of course, you should go.

572
00:33:49,470 --> 00:33:51,220
I have a more important task.

573
00:33:52,110 --> 00:33:54,320
Yang Minghua is managing government affairs tomorrow.

574
00:33:54,320 --> 00:33:55,320
Time is precious.

575
00:33:57,310 --> 00:33:58,840
Hurry up and come back soon.

576
00:33:59,230 --> 00:34:00,100
Go now.

577
00:34:10,590 --> 00:34:12,690
It's time to face Ning.

578
00:34:22,230 --> 00:34:22,949
My Lady.

579
00:34:25,429 --> 00:34:27,550
My Lady, Lord Xiu is back.

580
00:34:29,260 --> 00:34:31,320
He's coming this way. Stop drinking.

581
00:34:31,429 --> 00:34:32,719
Who is Lord Xiu?

582
00:34:33,090 --> 00:34:36,020
It's none of my business whether he comes back or not.

583
00:34:49,880 --> 00:34:50,510
My Lady.

584
00:34:58,860 --> 00:35:00,060
Who are you?

585
00:35:01,600 --> 00:35:03,920
Lord Xiu, you've gone too far.

586
00:35:04,040 --> 00:35:05,180
You've left for so long.

587
00:35:05,180 --> 00:35:06,840
Lady Ning has been suffering.

588
00:35:06,860 --> 00:35:08,250
She cried

589
00:35:08,440 --> 00:35:09,870
and drank every day.

590
00:35:14,750 --> 00:35:15,900
I'm Xiu.

591
00:35:17,270 --> 00:35:21,420
Brother Xiu, you're back.

592
00:35:21,780 --> 00:35:23,840
I've been waiting for you for so long.

593
00:35:23,870 --> 00:35:25,270
It's been seven years.

594
00:35:26,400 --> 00:35:29,910
Mei, your lady is drunk.

595
00:35:29,930 --> 00:35:31,330
Make some hangover soup.

596
00:35:31,670 --> 00:35:33,000
Yes, I'll be right back.

597
00:35:35,950 --> 00:35:36,670
Who are you?

598
00:35:37,550 --> 00:35:39,430
I'm Xiu.

599
00:35:40,340 --> 00:35:41,300
Zichuan Xiu.

600
00:35:42,750 --> 00:35:45,310
Fine, I shouldn't have pissed you off.

601
00:35:46,180 --> 00:35:48,510
I shouldn't have left you for seven years.

602
00:35:50,200 --> 00:35:54,200
It doesn't matter if you leave for a long time.

603
00:35:55,020 --> 00:35:55,990
Listen.

604
00:35:56,750 --> 00:35:58,990
You've been sending me things.

605
00:35:59,550 --> 00:36:01,210
People say they're rubbish.

606
00:36:01,360 --> 00:36:01,960
But...

607
00:36:03,740 --> 00:36:06,860
But I know these are all your treasures.

608
00:36:08,270 --> 00:36:10,790
Brother Xiu,

609
00:36:11,390 --> 00:36:14,190
you only hold it in your heart when you're wronged.

610
00:36:15,100 --> 00:36:18,300
When you were sad, you would smile to get it through.

611
00:36:19,120 --> 00:36:20,400
When you missed me,

612
00:36:20,730 --> 00:36:22,800
you would send me these treasures.

613
00:36:24,930 --> 00:36:26,730
Do you think I don't know?

614
00:36:32,110 --> 00:36:33,610
How could I not know?

615
00:36:39,750 --> 00:36:43,440
Brother Xiu, am I right?

616
00:36:47,530 --> 00:36:49,210
Sit down for a while.

617
00:36:50,870 --> 00:36:54,430
Don't throw up. Have some water.

618
00:36:55,230 --> 00:36:56,880
Here's the water. Here.

619
00:36:57,620 --> 00:36:58,260
Slowly.

620
00:37:02,190 --> 00:37:02,920
One more sip.

621
00:37:04,990 --> 00:37:06,100
Who are you?

622
00:37:14,120 --> 00:37:16,400
I'm Xiu. Zichuan Xiu.

623
00:37:18,330 --> 00:37:20,320
Why didn't you go home?

624
00:37:20,950 --> 00:37:22,390
I'm back now.

625
00:37:22,390 --> 00:37:23,510
No.

626
00:37:24,110 --> 00:37:27,910
You've been avoiding me since you came back to the Imperial Capital.

627
00:37:28,710 --> 00:37:30,310
If it weren't for Miss Baichuan,

628
00:37:30,310 --> 00:37:32,470
you wouldn't have come home.

629
00:37:32,830 --> 00:37:35,960
And every time I wanted to go shopping with you,

630
00:37:36,230 --> 00:37:37,510
you always avoided me.

631
00:37:38,480 --> 00:37:40,240
Do you think I want to play so much?

632
00:37:40,240 --> 00:37:41,580
That's because...

633
00:37:41,670 --> 00:37:42,230
I was wrong. I...

634
00:37:42,230 --> 00:37:44,560
You didn't do anything wrong. I was wrong.

635
00:37:45,220 --> 00:37:47,340
I thought I knew you the best.

636
00:37:48,320 --> 00:37:51,120
I really thought I knew you so well when I was young.

637
00:37:51,320 --> 00:37:53,140
I used to know what you were thinking

638
00:37:53,140 --> 00:37:54,940
and what you were talking about.

639
00:37:55,760 --> 00:37:57,620
But after you came back this time,

640
00:37:58,700 --> 00:37:59,990
I have no idea

641
00:38:00,400 --> 00:38:01,780
what you're thinking

642
00:38:01,930 --> 00:38:03,260
and what you care about.

643
00:38:07,610 --> 00:38:08,780
Brother Xiu.

644
00:38:11,620 --> 00:38:13,460
Do you not like me anymore?

645
00:38:15,150 --> 00:38:18,350
Do you hate me?

646
00:38:18,690 --> 00:38:20,600
I don't hate you. I just...

647
00:38:20,890 --> 00:38:24,100
Brother Xiu, you know what?

648
00:38:25,940 --> 00:38:27,450
I had been waiting so long

649
00:38:28,600 --> 00:38:30,190
for the duet.

650
00:38:31,610 --> 00:38:33,430
I was so happy.

651
00:38:35,510 --> 00:38:38,110
I chose the most beautiful dress.

652
00:38:38,830 --> 00:38:41,150
I also chose the best song.

653
00:38:45,470 --> 00:38:48,470
How could you forget it?

654
00:38:52,310 --> 00:38:53,270
You've changed.

655
00:38:54,200 --> 00:38:55,750
In the past,

656
00:38:56,820 --> 00:38:59,340
you always prioritized my matters.

657
00:39:00,190 --> 00:39:01,250
Okay, stop crying.

658
00:39:03,140 --> 00:39:05,910
Don't touch my fringe.

659
00:39:12,440 --> 00:39:14,390
You've changed.

660
00:39:14,420 --> 00:39:16,220
You don't care about me anymore.

661
00:39:17,590 --> 00:39:19,510
But I've changed too.

662
00:39:20,110 --> 00:39:21,510
In the past, I wouldn't be

663
00:39:23,160 --> 00:39:24,760
angry about these things.

664
00:39:26,310 --> 00:39:28,710
Didn't you just bring something delicious

665
00:39:28,710 --> 00:39:30,260
for Miss Baichuan?

666
00:39:30,870 --> 00:39:33,180
You just forgot to play.

667
00:39:33,200 --> 00:39:34,640
What's the big deal?

668
00:39:39,580 --> 00:39:42,970
But... But I...

669
00:39:44,030 --> 00:39:45,750
I mind.

670
00:39:46,740 --> 00:39:48,500
I feel sad.

671
00:39:50,040 --> 00:39:51,830
I'm petty.

672
00:40:03,300 --> 00:40:04,180
Brother Xiu.

673
00:40:06,010 --> 00:40:08,790
It's not good to grow up.

674
00:40:09,030 --> 00:40:10,340
I don't want to grow up.

675
00:40:14,890 --> 00:40:16,980
I don't want to like you anymore.

676
00:40:36,690 --> 00:40:37,530
Ning.

677
00:40:42,460 --> 00:40:43,130
Ning.

678
00:41:22,520 --> 00:41:24,560
How could I hate you?

679
00:41:26,440 --> 00:41:28,260
I hate myself.

680
00:41:32,600 --> 00:41:34,730
I hate myself for breaking my promise.

681
00:41:36,230 --> 00:41:37,190
I promised

682
00:41:37,190 --> 00:41:39,590
I would always be with you and protect you.

683
00:41:40,550 --> 00:41:43,190
But I left the Imperial Capital and you.

684
00:41:47,180 --> 00:41:49,080
I hate being timid.

685
00:41:50,400 --> 00:41:52,080
Every day in Yuanzhou,

686
00:41:52,170 --> 00:41:55,530
I wanted to write to you, but I dared not.

687
00:42:07,960 --> 00:42:09,600
You don't know how happy I was

688
00:42:10,460 --> 00:42:12,460
to come back to the Imperial Capital

689
00:42:13,260 --> 00:42:14,440
and to see you

690
00:42:16,850 --> 00:42:17,990
again.

691
00:42:20,560 --> 00:42:21,960
You seem to have grown up.

692
00:42:22,680 --> 00:42:25,360
Yet you seem to haven't changed at all.

693
00:42:26,620 --> 00:42:27,960
You're still the same.

694
00:42:30,710 --> 00:42:31,430
As for me,

695
00:42:33,800 --> 00:42:36,660
I don't know if I'm still the same person I used to be.

696
00:42:43,770 --> 00:42:45,590
I just don't want to live here.

697
00:42:46,770 --> 00:42:48,570
I don't dare to see you every day.

698
00:42:48,700 --> 00:42:49,840
As to what I'm saying now,

699
00:42:49,840 --> 00:42:51,240
I didn't dare to tell you.

700
00:43:01,790 --> 00:43:02,670
Ning.

701
00:43:33,310 --> 00:43:34,140
Ning.

702
00:43:35,410 --> 00:43:36,490
You're right.

703
00:43:38,390 --> 00:43:40,360
It's not happy to grow up.
